enter the address of the customer : asdfghj
enter the number of oil packets :1
enter the number of salt packets : 3
enter the number of sugar packets : 2
enter the number of soap packets : 0
enter the number of detergents : 4
customer phone number 9873646378
customer name devitejasri
customer address asdfghj
tax= 954.5
